<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12396] Document suggested use of log levels in dev guide</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12396</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now we don&apos;t provide any guidance on appropriate use of log levels, which leads to inconsistent use and in some cases exacerbating problems for tests and troubleshooting (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12395&quot; title=&quot;Some internal classes are logging to DEBUG what should be logged to TRACE&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-12395&quot;&gt;HBASE-12395&lt;/a&gt;). We should add a section on suggested use of log levels to the guide.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some related reading&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://watchitlater.com/blog/2009/12/logging-guidelines/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;a good ops-focused blog post on levels&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.codeproject.com/Articles/42354/The-Art-of-Logging&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;another, focused on devs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://stackoverflow.com/a/2031209&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;guidelines from a user on stackoverflow (that I like)&lt;/a&gt; also has some good discussion.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.javacodegeeks.com/2011/01/10-tips-proper-application-logging.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;extended logging discussion with some level use guidelines&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://developer.atlassian.com/display/CONFDEV/Logging+Guidelines&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;guidelines for Atlassian devs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.openstack.org/wiki/LoggingStandards&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;guidelines for OpenStack devs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://kafka.apache.org/coding-guide.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;the Kafka dev guide&lt;/a&gt; has a good section on their use titled &quot;Logging&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
